OL,3,CCouncils decide to push forward with
OL,4,Cproposals to create a regional mayor
OL,6,FCumbria's two councils have both
OL,7,Fagreed to ask the Government to create
OL,8,Fa mayor for the county.
OL,10,FCumberland Council and Westmorland
OL,11,FCouncil have jointly decided to join
OL,12,Fthe Government's Devolution Priority
OL,13,FProgramme, which aims to create
OL,14,Fgreater power for local authorities.
OL,16,FThe new Government aims to improve
OL,17,Fdecision-making by giving more local
OL,18,Fresponsibility to regions over issues
OL,19,Fsuch as transport, housing and
OL,20,Feconomic development.
