OL,3,CCouncils decide to push forward with
OL,4,Cproposals to create a regional mayor
OL,6,FLeader of the Westmorland and Furness
OL,7,FCouncil, Cllr Jonathan Brook, held a
OL,8,Fcabinet meeting putting the decision
OL,9,Fto a vote.
OL,11,FMeanwhile Cumberland Council Leader,
OL,12,FCllr Mark Fryer, agreed to sign a
OL,13,Fnotice stating their desire to be part
OL,14,Fof the devolution programme on 9
OL,15,FJanuary 2025.
OL,17,FToday's decision allows for the next
OL,18,Fstage of looking at a new strategic
OL,19,Fauthority for Cumbria, creating a
OL,20,Fposition for an elected Mayor.
