OL,3,CCouncils decide to push forward with
OL,4,Cproposals to create a regional mayor
OL,6,FA public consultation will be held
OL,7,Funder both council areas - becoming
OL,8,Fpart of a final decision later in the
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FA Cumbrian mayor would add further
OL,12,Fadditional responsibilities. It would
OL,13,Fnot take over from the current two
OL,14,Fcouncils which were formed in April
OL,15,F2023, to replace the former Cumbria
OL,16,FCounty Council and six district
OL,17,Fcouncils.
