OL,3,CCouncils decide to push forward with
OL,4,Cproposals to create a regional mayor
OL,6,FThe Leader of the Westmorland and
OL,7,FFurness Council, Cllr Jonathan Brook,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Some things are better done on
OL,9,Fa bigger geography than simply a local
OL,10,Fcouncil so we would have that.
OL,12,F"We'd also have a seat at the Mayoral
OL,13,FCouncil and the Council of Nations and
OL,14,FRegions.
OL,16,F"Clearly, if we don't have a seat at
OL,17,Fthat table then the voice of Cumbria
OL,18,Fwon't be heard - that won't do us any
OL,19,Ffavours at all."
