OL,3,CCouncils decide to push forward with
OL,4,Cproposals to create a regional mayor
OL,6,FDuring the Westmorland and Furness
OL,7,FCouncil cabinet meeting on 9 January
OL,8,F2025, some councillors did share
OL,9,Fconcerns that local authorities have
OL,10,Falready gone through recent changes.
OL,12,FThey also made claims that the
OL,13,FGovernment has not yet set out how
OL,14,Fmuch funding would be received for the
OL,15,Fextra responsibility.
OL,17,FCllr Mark Fryer, Leader of Cumberland
OL,18,FCouncil, said: "We have made it clear
OL,19,Fthat we want to be part of the
OL,20,Fdevolution discussion with Government.
